data.description: Impeccably cared for, this charming Cape Cod home boasts five bedrooms, two bathrooms, and a two-car attached garage with the potential for additional living space above. Nestled on a generously sized corner lot, it features an inviting front porch with captivating curb appeal. The interior is designed with an open-concept kitchen, living, and dining area, while the finished lower level showcases fresh flooring, newly applied paint, and ample storage space. Located in Rio, this residence offers a small-town lifestyle complete with favorable taxes, and convenient access to Portage, Columbus, Sun Prairie, and the Madison area for easy commuting.
